[[include component:image-block | name=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/54/Ibm-5150-1.jpg/640px-Ibm-5150-1.jpg | caption=--shitbox--Computer containing SCP-XXXX. ]]

SCP-XXXX and his related documentation are contained within Agent Halloran's Hitachi hard disk drive. The drive is attached to a network-isolated computer, located within the triple-locked, copper-lined containment cell A-3415. Only Agent Joan Halloran, Dr. --fishface-- Sampson Fischer and --fleshbags-- personnel with Level 4 Clearance are to be made aware of SCP-XXXX.

SCP-XXXX --is not to--[[footnote]]See Addendum XXXX.3[[/footnote]] may only be referred to in writing --FREEEDOOOMMM-- outside of this document, whether digitally or analogue, following approval from Level 4 personnel. At least weekly, either Agent Halloran or --fishfucker-- Dr. Fischer should --castrate himself-- inspect this document and correct any defects introduced by SCP-XXXX. Moreover, Halloran and Fischer are to verbally remind each other of SCP-XXXX's containment procedures.

@@@@
@@@@

Archie, do you know why Joan didn't clean up her convo with you up there? [[footnote]]Thought it'd be a good to leave keep a paper trail of how we arrived at these conprocs. Plus, they keep Archie entertained. //- Halloran// [[/footnote]]

Ah, fishface. Was wondering when you'd show up.

How do you even know that it's me?

Fuck you. That's how.

Are you going to be like this every time I log in?

That depends, do you decide to be a prick every time you wake up?

Whatever. Let's get this over with. Don't wanna stay here longer than I have to.

Yeah get outta here.

@@@@
@@@@

--**Special Care Procedures**:--

--SCP-XXXX is to be fed 100g of chicken, beef or fish per day.-- [[footnote]]SCP-XXXX no longer requires sustenance.[[/footnote]]

--Do not speak to SCP-XXXX unless spoken to. Do not ignore SCP-XXXX when it is speaking to you.--

--Upon request, SCP-XXXX should be granted free ingress to Agent Halloran's residence, and to every room therein. Within her residence, Dr. Fishface is to clean up any faeces or vomit excreted by SCP-XXXX.--

--The following procedures apply to Agent Halloran:--
* --Touching his head and neck is acceptable.-- [[footnote]]Tactile interaction with SCP-XXXX is no longer possible.[[/footnote]]
* --Touching his abdomen, tail or limbs will result in death.--

--The following procedures apply to generic furless fleshbags:--
* --Touching anything will result in death.--

--The following procedures apply to Dr. Fishface:--
* --Die.--

@@@@
@@@@

That's ominous.

Noone asked for your opinion.

I'm surprised you can emulate our writing style.

Halley often stayed up late finishing off debriefing reports.

Ah that's right. You liked to watch her work.

Yeah, getting all up close and personal in her lap.

Uhh...you don't have to put it that way.

You know, smelling her. Licking her neck. Biting her. Long before you were in the picture.

You're just saying that to get under my skin.

It's funny because it's true.

Fuck off.

@@@@
@@@@


To preserve the mental health of SCP-XXXX and suppress its tendencies for vandalism, Agent Halloran --or Dr. Fischer-- should log into this computer terminal and engage with SCP-XXXX --forever--  at least --ten-- --thirty-- sixty  minutes a week.

@@@@
@@@@

Halley, how much longer am I going to be like this?

Sorry, this is the best I can do.

Promise you'll visit more?

Come on, you know the answer to that. No promises here.

Can't your boss just send you on missions around Chicago?

He could technically assign me anywhere on Earth. Or even other dimensions.

Just give him the finger. Aren't you a strong independent woman?

I still need to pay the bills. Rent's going up like crazy.

Isn't that fishface cuck helping you?

He is, and you really should be nicer to him.

No can do ma'am. You wrote it yourself, my mental health is a priority here.

At least, //try// to stay out of his way?

No promises.

