To supplement the above activities, containment cell A-3415 should be furnished with an entertainment package, outlined below. Proposed contents must be first screened by RAISA staff and should be rotated at least once a month.

[[div class="blockquote"]]

++++ Entertainment Package (External) Iteration 45

@@@@

* A webcam is connected to this computer, so that SCP-XXXX is exposed to audiovisual feed in the cell.
* An odour meter is connected to this computer, so that SCP-XXXX is exposed to olfactory feed in the cell.
* A television broadcasts videos of rats, snakes, lizards and other species considered to be prey of SCP-XXXX. --Hnnnnggggg so close yet so far. why must you blue ball me like this-- 
* A DVD player continuously repeats a playlist consisting of ambient sounds typical of the Chicago suburbia.
* An aroma diffuser disperses a scent periodically varying between 60.00-65.00 on the Pungency Odour Index.
* --Internet access for freeeeeeedoooommm--

[[/div]]

