It's just, you're spending less and less time with me. Especially after Fischer came along.

He's my partner. He's going to be sticking around, whether you like it or not.

What good do you see in him anyway? You can do so much better.

Sam can be ineffectual at times, but he keeps me grounded. Keeps me sane in this insane world.



