++++ --Fuck. dogs.--

---Humanity's best friend...ha! They're just a bunch of disgusting brown-nosers. Always just sucking up to their fleshbag owners. Always trespassing in my hunting grounds, chasing balls and whatever the hell else fleshbags decide to throw around. Chase. Fetch. Chase. Fetch. Mindless dumbfucks.--

--There was this one fleshbag neighbour that took her retriever past our yard every day 8:00am sharp. It walked upright, tail always wagging, spittle dripping from its mouth. Like it owned the place. There was a 13% chance it would piss into our lawn. MY lawn. I had to piss over its piss to supplant the smell. God forbid it takes a dump. Good thing fishface takes care of it if I nag him enough.--

--And the barking. Oh my god, the barking. Is it that orgasmic to see any fleshbag that wonders by? Fucking attention whores. Can hardly get a good day's sleep.--

