Addendum: experiment log - Take him for walk outside to visit Patches. SCP-XXXX is inscribed on an Etch A Sketch.
* Initially thinks that it is to visit Archie Jr.
* How dare you walk me like a dog.
* Archie can see Patches, but Patches can't see him
* Owner of patches doesn't know why Halloran is rubbing the Etch A Sketch against Patches.
* Archie asks for a second visit
* Vandalism has been reduced.
